## 2. API (`apps/api`) — Nest / Prisma

### 2.1 Core

| Key | Required | Notes |
|-----|----------|--------|
| `NODE_ENV` | Production | `production` on Render |
| `PORT` | Optional | Default `4000`; Render sets automatically |
| `JWT_SECRET` | **Yes** (when auth enforced) | ≥ 32 random characters |
| `JWT_EXPIRES_IN` | Optional | e.g. `8h`, `12h`, `7d` |
| `DATABASE_URL` | Optional | Omit → embedded SQLite `apps/api/data/hub.db` |

### 2.2 Single-site + Google Sheet (recommended)

| Key | Required | Notes |
|-----|----------|--------|
| `HUB_SHEET_ONLY` | Recommended | `true` — Sheet login only; no DB user for JWT |
| `GOOGLE_SHEET_APPS_SCRIPT_URL` | **Yes** | Apps Script Web App `/exec` |
| `GOOGLE_SHEET_API_KEY` **or** `GOOGLE_SHEET_SITE_KEY` | **Yes** | Matches Script `API_KEY` or sheet `SITE_KEY` |
| `GOOGLE_SHEET_LOGIN_APPS_SCRIPT_URL` | Optional | Defaults to main URL |
| `SHEET_HUB_JWT_EMAIL` | Optional | Identity in JWT (e.g. owner email) |
| `SHEET_HUB_JWT_SUB` | Optional | Default `hub-sheet-owner` |
| `SHEET_HUB_JWT_ROLE` | Optional | `OWNER` or `MANAGER` |

### 2.3 HTTP / CORS / links

| Key | Notes |
|-----|--------|
| `PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL` | Public API origin for receipt URLs written to Sheets |
| `CORS_ORIGINS` | Comma-separated allowed browser origins |

### 2.4 Auth toggles

| Key | Notes |
|-----|--------|
| `OWNER_SETUP_SECRET` | Header `X-Setup-Secret` for `POST /auth/seed-owner` in production |
| `REQUIRE_API_AUTH` | `true` to require JWT outside production |
| `API_AUTH_DISABLED` | `true` **local only** — never on public internet |

### 2.5 Integrations

| Key | Header / usage |
|-----|----------------|
| `INTEGRATION_WEBHOOK_SECRET` | `X-Webhook-Secret` |
| `FINAL_ORDER_SUBMIT_SECRET` | `X-Final-Order-Secret` |

### 2.6 Storage (Cloudflare R2)

