## 3. Web (`apps/web`) — `NEXT_PUBLIC_*`

| Key | Notes |
|-----|--------|
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` | Empty = same origin; else full API base URL |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_JR_SHEET_APPS_SCRIPT_URL` | Browser `/exec` URL (align with API) |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_JR_WORKERS_CALENDAR_APPS_SCRIPT_URL` | Optional calendar script |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_SHEET_WEB_LOGIN` | `0` / `false` to prefer API login only |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_SKIP_HUB_LOGIN` | Dev only — skip login gate |

