## 4. Google Apps Script (not in `.env`)

Set in **Apps Script → Project settings → Script properties**:

| Property | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `API_KEY` | Must match `GOOGLE_SHEET_API_KEY` (if using API key auth) |
| `JR_SPREADSHEET_ID` | Bound sheet ID |
| `RECEIPTS_FOLDER_ID` | Optional override; default folder ID in `Code.gs` if unset |
| `INVOICES_FOLDER_ID` | If used by script |

Sheet **Config** tab may include `SITE_KEY` → matches `GOOGLE_SHEET_SITE_KEY` when using site-key auth.

